\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Editor }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 NLR }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 1960-61
. Found it very hard to negotiate with the Board. Clubs also pressing for influence, wanting something more immediate and campaigning. They had a big joint meeting at Leeds. Stuart decided he did not want to go down that path, resigned.}{\rtlch\fcs1 
