\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 23 April 2012}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
