\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Activities outside work}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 When young, sport, especially tennis and squash. Also played football and cricket. Supports Arsenal. Watches sport on TV: \lquote the competitive body\rquote 
. Enjoys cinema. Hard to distinguish work and play. Watches thrillers and melodrama. Reads popular novels. Sees popular culture and a \lquote contradictory space\rquote  rather than \lquote authentic expression\rquote  of working people\rquote .}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
