\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Friends and family}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Long-term friends. Breach through leaving Jamaica. When went back 1970s got to know some younger
 people from his school: David Scott, Hugh and Richard Spaull. But now sees rarely. In England, especially Mike Rustin, married to Catherine\rquote s sister. At student house in Oxford got to know West Indians who returned early in independence \endash 
 Scotty Lewis, Dodd Jermaine, Willy Demas, [Ridge Alleyne]. Again, see rarely, but remain in his head. Oxford friend, literary critics, also at OU [Graeme Martin]. Othe
r English friends from Oxford days, eg Tessa who had a mixed child and adopted black children. Political people from 1960s: Suzie Benghait, life-long friend from New Left. Students from 1970s, sees more often: Tony Jefferson, John Clarke, Charles Crit
cher. But new friends at each stage rather than life-long friends. When moved to London 1990s, new group of friends, feminists: Barbara Taylor, Sally Alexander. [Also Bill Schwarz, Greg Maclennan]}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Radical break with family of origin. 1964 married Catherine. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Becky}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844  born 1964 (while they were in student occupation), }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Jess}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844  born 1970. Girl and boy, as had wanted. Thrilled by birth, besotted by infant Becky. Seaside holidays in Cornwall. Becky, Jess, Catherine, her sister Margaret among closest familiars, \lquote inner core\rquote .
 And adores both grandchildren.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Becky}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844  trained at Tavistock, became analytic child psychotherapist. Split from boyfriend Amaury 
with whom had son Noah; now with Simon, youth worker. Stuart helped especially when Noah was young.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Jess}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844  tried anthropology, switched to Camberwell Art School and then St Martin\rquote 
s. Works in film and photography. New York Summer School proved start of successful career, making films, mainly commercial but also feature films, e.g. on Darwin, Marley. Married to Radha [Singh], one 
boy, Ishan. Travelling a lot. They are now living in Santa Monica.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
