\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844\charrsid1315844 Personally, best thing is marriage to Catherine. 14 years younger, just 18 when they met - \lquote I stole her youth\rquote . Earl
ier, he was more recognised than her; with feminism, she asserted herself.  Stuart had been a \lquote lost soul\rquote  and \lquote she absolutely saved my life\rquote .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1315844 
